@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="container mt-5">
    <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
    <p class="lead">Your privacy is important to us. This policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information.</p>

    <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>We may collect personal information such as your name, email address, and usage data to enhance your experience.</p>

    <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>We use your information to provide services, improve our platform, and communicate with you.</p>

    <h2>3. Data Protection</h2>
    <p>We implement security measures to protect your personal data. However, no online service is completely secure.</p>

    <h2>4. Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>We may use third-party services that collect data for analytics, advertising, or other purposes.</p>

    <h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You have the right to access, modify, or request deletion of your personal data.</p>

    <h2>6. Updates to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy. Any changes will be posted on this page.</p>

    <p class="mt-4">&copy; @DateTime.Now.Year YourWebsiteName. All rights reserved.</p>
</div>